title: Slapstick (1997)
description:
A farewell tribute to this popular Chicago ska-punk band. Members of SLAPSTICK would go on to play in a ton of other bands, including THE LAWRENCE ARMS, ALKALINE TRIO, and DUVALL. Includes their whole collection of memorable songs plus EIGHT previously unreleased tracks! Think Jawbreaker meets Operation Ivy.
